<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | Mohaa Finest Curtains</title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>">
    <meta name="keywords" content="<%= typeof keywords !== 'undefined' ? keywords : 'blackout curtains Nairobi, custom blackout curtains Kenya' %>">
    <meta name="author" content="Mohaa Finest Curtains">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="geo.region" content="KE-30">
    <meta name="geo.placename" content="Eastleigh, Nairobi">
    <meta name="geo.position" content="-1.2767;36.8219">
    <meta name="ICBM" content="-1.2767, 36.8219">
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= canonicalUrl %>">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= canonicalUrl %>">
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= title %>">
    <meta property="og:description" content="<%= description %>">
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= ogImage %>">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Mohaa Finest Curtains">
    <meta property="og:locale" content="en_KE">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= title %>">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="<%= description %>">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= ogImage %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.jpeg" type="image/jpeg">
    <%- include('partials/json-ld') %>
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Service",
      "name": "Custom Blackout Curtains Nairobi",
      "description": "Professional blackout curtain supply and installation for bedrooms, home theaters and nurseries across Nairobi and Eastleigh.",
      "provider": { "@id": "<%= baseUrl %>/#curtainstore" },
      "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Nairobi" },
      "url": "<%= canonicalUrl %>"
    }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <img src="/images/logo.jpeg" alt="Mohaa Finest Curtains Logo" class="logo">
                <span class="brand-name">Mohaa Finest Curtains</span>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-menu">
                <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
                <a href="/collections" class="nav-link">Collections</a>
                <a href="/services" class="nav-link">Services</a>
                <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
                <a href="/blog" class="nav-link">Curtain Tips</a>
                <a href="/how-it-works" class="nav-link">How It Works</a>
                <a href="/gallery" class="nav-link">Gallery</a>
                <a href="/faq" class="nav-link">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
            </div>
            <div class="mobile-menu-toggle"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="page-hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Custom Blackout Curtains in Nairobi</h1>
                <p>Complete light-blocking solutions for bedrooms, home theaters, and nurseries — tailored fabrics, velvet weights, and overlapping track systems installed by Eastleigh's curtain experts.</p>
                <a href="https://wa.me/<%= phoneIntl %>?text=I%20want%20custom%20blackout%20curtains%20in%20Nairobi" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Get Blackout Quote</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="landing-content">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="landing-grid">
                    <div class="landing-text">
                        <h2>Why Blackout Curtains Matter in Nairobi</h2>
                        <p>Nairobi's bright mornings and street lighting can disrupt sleep, screen time, and nursery routines. Custom blackout curtains from Mohaa Finest Curtains block up to 99% of incoming light while adding a layer of thermal insulation — keeping rooms cooler during the day and warmer at night.</p>
                        <p>Whether you are furnishing a master bedroom in Kilimani, a home theater in Karen, or a guest room in Eastleigh, our team measures on-site and recommends the right fabric weight, lining, and track configuration for your windows.</p>

                        <h2>Fabric Selections &amp; Velvet Weights</h2>
                        <p>We stock premium blackout fabrics ranging from mid-weight polyester blends to heavy velvet drapes that drape elegantly and absorb sound. Choose from solid neutrals, textured weaves, and rich jewel tones that complement modern and classic Kenyan interiors alike.</p>
                        <p>Every blackout panel is lined with a dedicated light-blocking layer and finished with reinforced hems designed to withstand daily use. For nurseries and children's rooms, we offer easy-care, fade-resistant fabrics that maintain their colour after repeated washing.</p>

                        <h2>Custom Overlapping Tracks &amp; Professional Installation</h2>
                        <p>Light leaks around curtain edges are a common problem with off-the-shelf solutions. Our custom overlapping track systems ensure panels meet in the centre with minimal gaps, and side returns seal light along the wall. We install ceiling-mounted tracks, wall brackets, and motorised options for wide sliding doors.</p>
                        <p>From free measurement at your home to final fitting, Mohaa Finest Curtains handles the entire process. Visit our showroom at Moyale Mall, General Waruinge St, Eastleigh, or <a href="/contact">book a free measurement</a> via WhatsApp. Also explore our <a href="/sheer-curtains">sheer curtains</a> for layered day-and-night window styling.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="landing-image">
                        <img src="/images/blackout-curtains.jpg" alt="Custom blackout curtains installed in a Nairobi bedroom">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="landing-features">
                    <div class="landing-feature-card">
                        <h3>Bedroom Sleep Solutions</h3>
                        <p>Total darkness for deeper rest — ideal for shift workers and light-sensitive sleepers across Nairobi.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="landing-feature-card">
                        <h3>Home Theater Rooms</h3>
                        <p>Block glare on screens with heavy velvet panels and side-return tracks for cinema-quality darkness.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="landing-feature-card">
                        <h3>Thermal &amp; Sound Benefits</h3>
                        <p>Thick blackout linings reduce heat gain and dampen street noise — a practical upgrade for urban homes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="final-cta">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready for Total Light Control?</h2>
                <p>Book a free measurement and get a custom blackout curtain quote for your Nairobi home.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/<%= phoneIntl %>?text=I%20want%20custom%20blackout%20curtains%20for%20my%20bedroom" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">WhatsApp for Quote</a>
                    <a href="/collections" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Collections</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Mohaa Finest Curtains</h3>
                    <p><strong>Think Curtains. Think Mohaa.</strong></p>
                    <p>Moyale Mall, General Waruinge St, Eastleigh, Nairobi, Kenya</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Specialty Pages</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/blackout-curtains">Blackout Curtains</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/sheer-curtains">Sheer Curtains</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/office-blinds">Office Blinds</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/collections">All Collections</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Contact</h3>
                    <p>📞 <%= phone %></p>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/<%= phoneIntl %>" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">WhatsApp Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Mohaa Finest Curtains. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <a href="https://wa.me/<%= phoneIntl %>?text=Hi%20Mohaa%20Finest%20Curtains,%20I%20need%20blackout%20curtains" class="whatsapp-sticky" target="_blank" aria-label="Contact us on WhatsApp">
        <img src="/images/logo.jpeg" alt="WhatsApp Mohaa Finest Curtains" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;">
    </a>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
